<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 00:33:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>大棒而非胡萝卜：国际刑事法院之争表明全球对顽固的以色列不耐烦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-27/ty-article-opinion/.premium/sticks-not-carrots-icc-battle-signals-global-impatience-with-intransigent-israel/0000018f-baad-df3d-abbf-bffd33e30000</link><description>就连以色列的盟友也不认为其政府能够应对加沙战争，这促使以色列采取制裁定居者、冻结军事援助等行动，现在还可能对以色列的拉法行动发出国际刑事法院的逮捕令和国际法院的命令</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 20:37:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-27/ty-article-opinion/.premium/sticks-not-carrots-icc-battle-signals-global-impatience-with-intransigent-israel/0000018f-baad-df3d-abbf-bffd33e30000</guid></item><item><title>即使没有人质协议，拉法的平民死亡也可能迫使以色列停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/civilian-deaths-in-rafah-could-force-israel-into-a-cease-fire-even-without-a-hostage-deal/0000018f-bba5-d5c5-a3ff-fbad95c50000</link><description>以色列国防军正在向城市推进，但即使是强制撤离也没有解决密集地区的作战问题，看来部队的压力是行动的主要困难</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 20:23:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/civilian-deaths-in-rafah-could-force-israel-into-a-cease-fire-even-without-a-hostage-deal/0000018f-bba5-d5c5-a3ff-fbad95c50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列新征兵部队被派往加沙贾巴利亚，只受过最低限度的训练</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-new-israeli-army-conscripts-sent-to-gazas-jabalya-with-minimal-training/0000018f-bb40-dc1f-abef-ff79e0270000</link><description>“他们到达时有点震惊，但几天后，爆炸就成了家常便饭”：当新武装的以色列国防军新兵通常仍在训练时，他们现在发现自己身处加沙战场的中心</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 20:07:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-new-israeli-army-conscripts-sent-to-gazas-jabalya-with-minimal-training/0000018f-bb40-dc1f-abef-ff79e0270000</guid></item><item><title>欧洲外交官警告拉法罢工将加大对以色列接受停火的压力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/european-diplomats-warn-rafah-strike-could-lead-to-strict-interpretation-of-icj-orders/0000018f-bb65-d5c5-a3ff-fb6dd0720000</link><description>尽管国际法院上周限制以色列在拉法行动的命令“足够模糊，足以让各国能够视而不见”，但欧洲外交官警告说，以色列从夜间到周一对拉法的致命袭击可能会改变局面</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 19:35:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/european-diplomats-warn-rafah-strike-could-lead-to-strict-interpretation-of-icj-orders/0000018f-bb65-d5c5-a3ff-fb6dd0720000</guid></item><item><title>庆祝拉法巴勒斯坦人死亡的右翼分子是以色列的“真面目”吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-27/ty-article/.highlight/are-right-wingers-celebrating-palestinian-deaths-in-rafah-the-true-face-of-israel/0000018f-baee-dfb0-a7af-fbfe52ac0000</link><description>有人说，这才是以色列真正的丑恶嘴脸。那些相信并且了解一个不同的以色列的人面临着证明事实并非如此的不可能的挑战</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 19:20:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-27/ty-article/.highlight/are-right-wingers-celebrating-palestinian-deaths-in-rafah-the-true-face-of-israel/0000018f-baee-dfb0-a7af-fbfe52ac0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列电视曝光揭露内塔尼亚胡主要部长涉嫌严重腐败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-tv-expose-uncovers-alleged-deep-corruption-of-key-netanyahu-minister/0000018f-bab5-d0b7-abdf-feb7c40f0000</link><description>以色列警察和总检察长等众多观众热切观看了交通部长米里·雷格夫的两集电视特别节目，并宣布他们正在调查她在任期间的行为</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 17:47:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-tv-expose-uncovers-alleged-deep-corruption-of-key-netanyahu-minister/0000018f-bab5-d0b7-abdf-feb7c40f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼部长本-格维尔传唤警察局长进行谴责，尽管他无权这样做</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/israeli-minister-ben-gvir-summons-top-cop-for-reprimand-despite-lacking-authority-to-do-so/0000018f-baf5-d19e-a19f-fef734af0000</link><description>以色列国家安全部长在给该专员的一封信中声称，“最近对你总体功能失调的指控越来越多”，并补充说，“你唯一做得好的事情就是提拔与你关系密切的官员”</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 17:22:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/israeli-minister-ben-gvir-summons-top-cop-for-reprimand-despite-lacking-authority-to-do-so/0000018f-baf5-d19e-a19f-fef734af0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 234 天：哈马斯称因拉法死亡将不会参加停战谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-234-hamas-says-it-wont-attend-truce-talks-because-of-rafah-deaths/0000018f-bae3-d5c5-a3ff-fbeb99740001</link><description>以色列国防军证实，拉法针对哈马斯高级成员的袭击导致附近帐篷营地起火，造成 45 名平民死亡 ■ 埃及士兵在拉法过境点与以色列军队发生冲突时丧生 ■ 卡塔尔外交部：以色列对拉法的袭击可能会阻碍停战谈判 ■ 哈马斯消息来源称由于拉法的死亡而不会参加谈判 ■ 战争进入 234 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 16:37:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-234-hamas-says-it-wont-attend-truce-talks-because-of-rafah-deaths/0000018f-bae3-d5c5-a3ff-fbeb99740001</guid></item><item><title>埃及士兵在拉法边境口岸附近与以色列军队交火时丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/egyptian-soldier-killed-in-exchange-of-fire-with-israeli-army-near-rafah-border-crossing/0000018f-baab-d0b7-abdf-febf2ddb0000</link><description>以色列军队根据士兵的目击者描述评估，一名埃及士兵首先向以色列国防军士兵开枪；埃及军方表示已对事件展开调查</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 15:57:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/egyptian-soldier-killed-in-exchange-of-fire-with-israeli-army-near-rafah-border-crossing/0000018f-baab-d0b7-abdf-febf2ddb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院将讨论关闭以色列加沙囚犯拘留中心</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-to-discuss-closure-of-israeli-detention-center-for-inmates-from-gaza/0000018f-ba2d-d33c-a5bf-ff3d2b1e0000</link><description>近几个月有报道称该设施的条件可能违反以色列和国际法，以色列人权组织向以色列最高法院请愿，要求关闭关押加沙被拘留者的斯德泰曼设施</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 15:12:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-to-discuss-closure-of-israeli-detention-center-for-inmates-from-gaza/0000018f-ba2d-d33c-a5bf-ff3d2b1e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列裔阿拉伯妇女死于枪伤；以色列中部发现一名男子死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-arab-woman-dies-of-gunshot-wounds-man-found-dead-in-central-israel/0000018f-ba2c-d06c-a3ff-be3d898a0000</link><description>警方正在调查以色列中部发生的两起独立死亡事件，他们认为这起案件本质上是犯罪行为</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 14:43:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-arab-woman-dies-of-gunshot-wounds-man-found-dead-in-central-israel/0000018f-ba2c-d06c-a3ff-be3d898a0000</guid></item><item><title>这是以色列面临的最大威胁。这不是哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-is-the-greatest-threat-facing-israel-its-not-hamas/0000018f-b929-d24f-a5df-ffef4c4f0000</link><description>以色列正在进行第二次独立战争，同时面临生存威胁。但这种威胁来自我们内部</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 14:07:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-is-the-greatest-threat-facing-israel-its-not-hamas/0000018f-b929-d24f-a5df-ffef4c4f0000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷大卫城发现 2,300 年前的儿童尺寸金戒指</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-05-27/ty-article/child-size-gold-ring-found-in-jerusalems-city-of-david-from-2-300-years-ago/0000018f-ba09-dca9-a5cf-be0907070000</link><description>在同一层中发现的其他黄金珠宝更令人印象深刻，但这本身就很好，嵌入了深红色的石头</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 13:35:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-05-27/ty-article/child-size-gold-ring-found-in-jerusalems-city-of-david-from-2-300-years-ago/0000018f-ba09-dca9-a5cf-be0907070000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高级军事律师正在调查加沙战争期间大约 70 起可能的违法行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/top-idf-lawyer-investigating-about-70-possible-violations-during-gaza-war/0000018f-b9cb-df13-a3af-bddf0d610000</link><description>以色列军法署署长表示，虽然以色列国防军获得了如何依法实现其战争目标的法律建议，但“在如此规模和强度的战争中，严重事件时有发生”</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 13:29:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/top-idf-lawyer-investigating-about-70-possible-violations-during-gaza-war/0000018f-b9cb-df13-a3af-bddf0d610000</guid></item><item><title>他曾在加沙引导以色列游客：“我们的好奇心变成了盲目”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/he-used-to-guide-israeli-tourists-in-gaza-our-curiosity-turned-into-blindness/0000018f-b49e-dfc6-a3ef-b5de42d90000</link><description>加沙和约旦河西岸曾经是以色列最早也是最知名的导游之一塞菲·本·约瑟夫最常访问的目的地之一。回想起来，他意识到把以色列游客带到那里是多么错误</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 12:38:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/he-used-to-guide-israeli-tourists-in-gaza-our-curiosity-turned-into-blindness/0000018f-b49e-dfc6-a3ef-b5de42d90000</guid></item><item><title>战后巴勒斯坦权力机构还会继续管理加沙吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/will-the-palestinian-authority-even-be-around-to-govern-gaza-after-the-war/0000018f-ba01-dca9-a5cf-be0133580000</link><description>财政部长贝扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇和以色列极右翼决心在巴勒斯坦权力机构有机会从哈马斯手中接管飞地之前让其破产</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 12:35:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/will-the-palestinian-authority-even-be-around-to-govern-gaza-after-the-war/0000018f-ba01-dca9-a5cf-be0133580000</guid></item><item><title>将以色列踢出国际足联可能有助于结束加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-27/ty-article-opinion/.premium/kicking-israel-out-of-fifa-could-help-end-the-gaza-war/0000018f-b9aa-dcd7-abff-bdabda3c0000</link><description>我们看到国际压力对以色列政府的影响有限，但在内塔尼亚胡支持者过多的足球阵营中，文化制裁的力量可能会产生前所未有的影响</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 11:54:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-27/ty-article-opinion/.premium/kicking-israel-out-of-fifa-could-help-end-the-gaza-war/0000018f-b9aa-dcd7-abff-bdabda3c0000</guid></item><item><title>“节日快乐”：右翼以色列记者庆祝拉法袭击，将其比作 Lag Ba&amp;#39;Omer 篝火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/right-wing-israeli-journalists-celebrate-rafah-attack-likening-it-to-lag-baomer-bonfire/0000018f-b983-dca9-a5cf-bd832e6e0000</link><description>据巴勒斯坦卫生工作者称，以色列记者伊农·马加尔(Yinon Magal)在谈到以色列对加沙南部拉法的袭击时表示，“今年拉法的中心篝火造成至少35人死亡”</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 11:06:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/right-wing-israeli-journalists-celebrate-rafah-attack-likening-it-to-lag-baomer-bonfire/0000018f-b983-dca9-a5cf-bd832e6e0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔违反高等法院命令，绕过警察局长下令停职警察</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/violating-high-court-order-ben-gvir-bypasses-police-chief-to-order-suspension-of-cops/0000018f-b929-d24f-a5df-ffef236f0000</link><description>尽管警察局长已经亲自下令停职，但本格维尔绕过他的权力，直接去找边防警察局长。在他与部长之间日益紧张的情况下，最高警察将这个问题提交给司法部长，这是前所未有的举动</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 10:49:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/violating-high-court-order-ben-gvir-bypasses-police-chief-to-order-suspension-of-cops/0000018f-b929-d24f-a5df-ffef236f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列称拉法平民可能死于袭击哈马斯官员引发的火灾；死亡人数达45人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/eu-israel-continues-military-action-despite-icj-order-u-s-looks-into-rafah-attack/0000018f-b89e-df13-a3af-bc9ef6450000</link><description>巴勒斯坦人报告称，加沙流离失所者的帐篷遭到袭击，造成 45 人死亡；以色列军队声称这次袭击针对的是哈马斯官员，并正在调查“无关个人”遭到袭击的报道；欧盟最高外交官要求以色列执行国际法院对拉法的裁决</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 06:42:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/eu-israel-continues-military-action-despite-icj-order-u-s-looks-into-rafah-attack/0000018f-b89e-df13-a3af-bc9ef6450000</guid></item></channel></rss>